  "url": "https://www.lankadeepa.lk/news/\u0da2\u0db1\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2-\u0db1\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dc3\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca-\u0dbb\u0da7-\u0db6\u0dd3\u0db8-\u0d89\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dc3\u0dd6-\u0d85\u0dbb\u0d9c\u0dbd\u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dcf-\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dca\u0da9\u0dca/101-619028",
  "time_ut": 1661877463,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0da2\u0db1\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0db1\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dc3\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0dbb\u0da7 \u0db6\u0dd3\u0db8 \u0d89\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dc3\u0dd6 \u0d85\u0dbb\u0d9c\u0dbd\u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dcf \u0dbb\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dca\u0da9\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The activist who poured country drinks from the President's residence was remanded",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Fort Magistrate Thilina Gamage ordered today (30) to remand a person who allegedly entered the private house of President Ranil Wickramasinghe and brought out bottles of foreign liquor during the struggle, until he is presented in an identification parade.",
        "The Criminal Investigation Department presented the facts to the court that the suspect was arrested on the basis of photos and information released on social media while breaking into the President's residence with a stolen bottle of foreign liquor.",
        "The Criminal Investigation Department informed the court that investigations were conducted on this suspect based on the statements given by a suspect who had previously been presented to the court in relation to this incident."
      ],
